trans-unit.source: Represents an admissible value of an <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en admissible verdien for en <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Default constructor.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktør.

trans-unit.source: Required for XAML deserialization.
trans-unit.target: Kreves for XAML deserialisering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the list of arguments for this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir argumentlisten for dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfrie.

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of arguments.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer listen over argumenter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the description of this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty"></xref> for use by a prospective UI client.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir beskrivelsen av dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty"> </xref> for bruk av en potensiell UI-klient.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional and is culture-sensitive.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfri, og er kultur sikkerhetsfølsom.

trans-unit.source: Returns the description.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer beskrivelsen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name that can be used by a prospective UI client to display this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på som kan brukes av en potensiell UI-klient for å vise dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional and is culture-sensitive.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfri, og er kultur sikkerhetsfølsom.

trans-unit.source: When this property is not set, it is assigned the same value as the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue.Name%2A> property (and, therefore, would not be localized).
trans-unit.target: Når denne egenskapen ikke er angitt, tilordnes samme verdi som den <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue.Name%2A>egenskapen (og vil derfor ikke lokaliseres).</xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the name.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer navnet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets Help information for this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir hjelpeinformasjon for dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Can be used to specify a Help URL.
trans-unit.target: Kan brukes til å angi en hjelpe URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional and is culture-sensitive.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfri, og er kultur sikkerhetsfølsom.

trans-unit.source: Returns the Help information.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer hjelp.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that determines whether this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"></xref> is the default value for the associated <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som bestemmer om dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"> </xref> er standardverdien for den tilknyttede <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional and its default value is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfri, og standardverdien er `false`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the enum value is the default value; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis enum-verdi er standardverdi. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets additional attributes of this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir flere attributter for dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property can be used as a grab bag for additional metadata of this value that are not captured by the primary fields.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan brukes som en grab samling for flere metadata for denne verdien ikke er registrert av de primære feltene.

trans-unit.source: A custom UI is required to interpret the additional metadata because the included UI formats are not aware of them.
trans-unit.target: En egendefinert brukergrensesnitt kreves for å tolke flere metadata fordi inkludert UI-formater ikke er klar over dem.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfrie.

trans-unit.source: Returns the additional attributes.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer flere attributter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of this <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på dette <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This field is mandatory and culture-invariant.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er obligatorisk og kulturen konstant.

trans-unit.source: Returns the name.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer navnet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a switch representation of this property for the case when the parent <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"></xref> represents a tool parameter.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en switch representasjon av denne egenskapen for tilfeller når overordnet <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"> </xref> representerer en verktøyet-parameter.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional and culture-invariant.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfritt og kulturen konstant.

trans-unit.source: Returns the switch representation.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer switch representasjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the prefix for the switch representation of this value for the case when the parent <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"></xref> represents a tool parameter.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir prefikset for bryteren-representasjon av verdien for tilfeller når overordnet <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumProperty"> </xref> representerer en verktøyet-parameter.

trans-unit.source: This field is optional and culture-invariant.
trans-unit.target: Dette feltet er valgfritt og kulturen konstant.

trans-unit.source: Returns the switch prefix.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer switch prefiks.
